Hello,

Perhaps you could try expressions such as :

(1) -> reduce(*,[eval(1+j, j=k) for k in [p[i] for i in 1..2]])

   (1)  (p  + 1)p  + p  + 1
          1      2    1
                                                     Type: Polynomial Integer
(2) -> reduce(+,[eval(1+j, j=k) for k in [p[i] for i in 1..2]])

   (2)  p  + p  + 2
         2    1
                                                     Type: Polynomial Integer

Sincerely,
Steve


